Package: TRACLUS
Title: Trajectory Clustering via Partition-and-Group Framework
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Martin", "Hoblisch", , "martin.hoblisch@tu-dresden.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the TRACLUS algorithm for trajectory clustering
    based on the partition-and-group framework proposed by Lee, Han & Whang (2007).
    Trajectories are partitioned into line segments using the Minimum Description
    Length (MDL) principle, and similar segments are grouped using a 
    density-based clustering approach.
